{
  "stem": "24515.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "However, this young man had to put this on my desk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, who did this?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he stuck his face into mine and said, I did, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I thought myself, look, might just as well be knocked about one way as the other.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I fetched out and gave him the most satisfying smack in the face I have ever done.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it seemed like nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I expected the classroom to go after me, but it didn't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Indeed, the particular young man came and asked me back for the and when my back was turned, he cleaned up the desk and so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were afraid, especially of the teachers, who they thought would support me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's a sequence to this story, which I learned much later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I happened to be out with my mother to visit some of her friends, and mother then was talking to me, oh yes, this is so and so, the heroic Walter.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, how am I heroic Walter, you see?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I got it out of my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She didn't want to tell us this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the boy whom I had hit, his father was a Stormtroop officer, a Stormtroop bigshot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he called my father and he said he didn't appreciate his son being attacked by, you know, by this Jewish pig or whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father apparently told him very quietly that he never interferes in his son's school problems, but he was pleased to hear that he was able to stand up for himself, and hung up.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
